CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

December 21, 2010

[Cite as 12/2112010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-6281.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2002-1380. Disciplinary Counsel v. Brown.

This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing of a motion for an order to appear and show cause by relator. On December 12, 2010, respondent filed a motion to strike the motion to appear and show cause. Upon consideration thereof,

It is ordered that respondent’s motion to strike is denied.
